{"tid":1514474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[入黎睇睇]開始懷疑中共水軍想散播謠言主動帶風向嚇走示威者","createTime":"2019-08-28T18:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T04:18:40.000Z","uid":67294,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b70c70beba93320adc2fde673ed4886ac07c4f5","tid":1514474,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:01:42.000Z","msg":"呢排愈黎愈多果啲示威者比人毒打/強姦既謠言<br />\n首先我唔係話所有都一定係假, 但我就咁睇有好多放料既手法都同大陸水軍好似<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大陸因為信息封鎖, 佢地玩輿論同帶風向係玩到熟哂</strong>, 通常都係玩啲綜藝節目果啲放料多<br />\n佢地將呢啲放料叫做<strong>&quot;放瓜&quot;</strong> (熟大陸文化既實聽過), 而最基本最低級既做法就係會cap張對話圖, 話個消息來源係佢朋友, 之後自己就會附和幾句, 大家睇下啲大陸例子:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=mm4ina/ctp-vzntr/89s4809n4r9o4o6o8o8550268q5s5o58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dmm4ina%2Fctp-vzntr%2F89s4809n4r9o4o6o8o8550268q5s5o58.jpg&h=c47be133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=15000uj/ctp-vzntr/r8o5q65n3p2644p6o1210n8q9rr2s63q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D15000uj%2Fctp-vzntr%2Fr8o5q65n3p2644p6o1210n8q9rr2s63q.jpg&h=22d53bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AADxEn0.img?h=351&amp;w=624&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAADxEn0.img%3Fh%3D351%26w%3D624%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df&h=7e9523c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講, 用對話圖同一唱一和黎放流料帶風向真係大陸常用手法, 而且基本人大陸人係己經免疫哂<br />\n佢地既做法就係<strong>一律對話圖都唔會信</strong><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日係連登開始見到人cap對話圖黎放料話義士比人暴力對待, 又話聽朋友講所以放料上黎<br />\n本人強烈建議呢啲都唔好盡信/流傳<br />\n<br />\n因為過往有哂實質證據既, <strong>極大多數都係經權威人士放出黎</strong>, 例如林卓庭單酷刑, 陳淑莊講呂小姐同埋荃灣比人斬既傷勢圖<br />\n再或者, 612反送中未有大陸關注之前, 所有放料既大多數都係有人好詳細講返事件經過, <strong>絕對唔會一句起兩句止</strong><br />\n而且<strong>我上連登咁多年真係未幾過有人放流料放對話圖</strong>, 呢啲手法咁似大陸水軍, 極有可能就係佢地落黎帶風向<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我知黑警依家真係咩都做得出, 但係信息咁混亂既時勢各位真係要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"00a907f216cb55b98880f01f3f2867b966cdd6c7","tid":1514474,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:03:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf54a27ba2152d4afc60495ad5de072a1de45579","tid":1514474,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:03:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511a6fa913c0a64ce6ad6cc94ba9e1647c3d8d58","tid":1514474,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:05:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42586de9a7168234c18ef7a9d06c445c2dd10ea","tid":1514474,"uid":22360,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:08:14.000Z","msg":"坦白講，我完全相信虐待/強暴呢啲事情係有發生，但問題在於我哋係冇資料來源嘅情況下不停咁樣討論有冇意義呢？就算呢啲事情係真，我哋又可以做到啲乜嘢呢？我諗唯一一樣野就係繼續抗爭，將心機擺返係尋找不同嘅出路上面，如果抗爭成功，自然會還受害者一個清白，而唔係浪費自己嘅精力同時間係一啲冇辦法證實嘅羅生門入面。"},{"pid":"c6ba888880c056c1582975e031a29b6d1d17fce7","tid":1514474,"uid":226421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"其實佢越咁做, 香港人就越唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要全世界睇住, 你估牆內咁咩<br />\n8319293"},{"pid":"86514993f85eca2f36ca1c97e20d4213bad07ab1","tid":1514474,"uid":67294,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b42586de9a7168234c18ef7a9d06c445c2dd10ea","tid":1514474,"uid":22360,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18